name: 5 bed detached house for sale
description: An imposing, over 2,300 square feet, freehold converted dairy in Haggerston, moments away from beautiful Albion Square, one of East London’s most prestigious garden squares. Formerly a working dairy, the property is arranged over four floors and offers a practical and flexible layout with five bedrooms to the first and second floors, having access to two private terraces; soundproofed music room/studio to the lower ground level; and a double height reception room with an additional gallery/mezzanine space.
